,"iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:42:40.507+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Monster Hunt","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Young monster kids try to make peace between the world of humans and the world of the monsters."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Chasseur de monstres","runtime":108,"tagline":"Les monstres sont devenus plus gros","homepage":"","overview":"Dans un passé lointain, monstres et hommes vivaient en paix, jusqu'au jour ou ces derniers chassèrent les monstres de leur terre. Profitant de la guerre civile engendrée, un ministre usurpe le trône du roi des monstres et veut se débarrasser de la reine et de son futur bébé. Les deux fugitifs bientôt pris au piège, n'ont d'autre choix que de se réfugier chez les hommes...."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Il regno di Wuba","runtime":0,"tagline":"Una nuova avventura di simpatici mostri","homepage":"","overview":"Uomini e mostri non possono convivere in armonia: i primi, per paura o per diletto, finiranno sempre per andare a caccia dei secondi. Consapevole di questo, la Regina dei Mostri, incinta e minacciata di morte, fa di tutto per preservare la salute del nascituro. Con una mossa disperata renderà gravido un umano, per giunta di sesso maschile: lo sciocco di buon cuore Song Tianyin. Saranno lui e la cacciatrice di mostri Xiaolan, tra mille vicissitudini, a dare alla luce il piccolo Wuba e poi a difenderlo da molteplici minacce."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"捉妖记","runtime":0,"tagline":"看黄b片网：4488𝟺𝟔𝟵.com","homepage":"","overview":"　　山雄伟，海辽阔，经奇幻。自古以来人妖共存于世，人欲主天下，妖遂被驱逐入山。其后历朝，妖偶有越界，皆由捉妖天师秘密处理。老妖王辞世，妖界大乱，众妖越界流窜，一时间世间人妖难辨。在偏安深山的永宁村中，村长宋天荫（井柏然 饰）偶遇一路逐妖而来的菜鸟天师霍小岚（白百何 饰），在意外共度一夜后，被妖后托胎，随即生下了小妖王胡巴。为了自己的私心，小岚带着天荫一路同行前往顺天府，保护他躲过各种妖怪，也渐渐与天荫及胡巴产生了感情。然而为时已晚，胡巴已落入坏人之手，为营救胡巴，小岚与天荫在众人的帮助下勇闯登仙楼，与大反派葛千户（钟汉良 饰）展开一场殊死对决……人妖相克，究竟谁主天下？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Охота на монстра","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Когда-то давно люди и демоны мирно сосуществовали, но затем человеческая жадность привела род демонов на грань исчезновения. Плодом страсти обычного парня Инь Тяня и таинственной незнакомки становится малыш, которому предначертано занять трон короля демонов. Теперь странноватой парочке придется защищать свое чадо от злых демонов и коварных людей. Главным их врагом становится жестокий и алчный Цянь Ху Гэ, стремящийся пленить будущего короля, чтобы обрести безмерную силу."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"ศึกถล่มฟ้า อสูรน้อยจอมซน","runtime":111,"tagline":"มอนสเตอร์ ฮันท์ : ศึกถล่มฟ้า อสูรน้อยจอมซน","homepage":"","overview":"ในโลกแห่งจินตนาการที่ไกลแสนไกล มนุษย์เตรียมกำลังทำสงครามกับเหล่าปีศาจเพื่อช่วงชิงดินแดน และในสงครามวันสุดท้ายเหล่าปีศาจก็เสียรู้มนุษย์ ถูกกวาดต้อนไปในหุบเขาที่มืดมิด ตั้งแต่นั้นมาเหล่าปีศาจก็ถูกกักขังไม่ให้เข้ามาในดินแดนอีก ทั้งสองเผ่าพันธุ์ต่างแยกกันอยู่ จนกระทั่งราชาปีศาจองค์ใหม่ได้ถือกำเนิดขึ้น เป็นราชาผู้ที่จะปรับสมดุลของอำนาจและจัดระเบียบโลกใหม่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Monster Hunt","runtime":111,"tagline":"Un Film de Raman Hui","homepage":"","overview":"El hijo de la realeza del clan de los monstruos es amenazado por los cazadores de criaturas que impiden que se mezclen con los humanos. El hijo de un famoso espadachín, pero poco dotado para el heroísmo, terminará siendo el encargado de proteger al heredero del trono, enfrentándose a monstruos malignos, cazamonstruos y otros enemigos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Lov na příšery","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kdysi dávno žili monstra vedle lidských obydlí. Lidé je jednoho dne porazili a oni utekli do vzdálených hor. Vytvořili si tam vlastní království, v kterém žijí dodnes. Když nějaké z nich z tohoto místa odešlo a zabloudilo mezi lidi, čekala ho smrt. Úřad pro lov monster odváděl tak dobrou práci, až lidé zapomněli, že monstra vůbec existovala. Tak to platilo až doteď."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"몬스터 헌트","runtime":0,"tagline":"하나의 세상, 두 개의 종족! 피할 수 없는 그들의 전쟁이 시작된다!","homepage":"","overview":"인간과 동물, 그리고 요괴가 함께 사는 먼 옛날. 인간과 요괴 사이에 큰 전쟁이 벌어지고 요괴 세계에 인간이 두려워할 새로운 후계자 '우바'가 태어난다. 이에 '우바'를 없애려는 인간과 원치 않은 사건(?)으로 '우바'의 부모가 된 요괴 잡는 몬스터 헌터와의 피할 수 없는 전쟁이 시작된다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Полювання на монстра","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Колись давно люди і демони мирно співіснували, але потім людська жадібність призвела рід демонів на грань зникнення... Плодом пристрасті звичайного хлопця Інь Тяня і таємничої незнайомки стає малюк, якому визначено зайняти трон короля демонів. Тепер дивнй парочці доведеться захищати своє чадо від злих демонів і підступних людей. Головним їхнім ворогом стає жорстокий і жадібний Цянь Ху Ге, прагнучий полонити майбутнього короля, щоб набути безмірну силу."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Upa – Meu Monstro Favorito","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em uma realidade na qual seres humanos e monstros coexistem, a rainha dos monstros engravida um humano. Da união nasce Huba, um híbrido entre as duas raças que enfrenta hostilidade vinda dos dois lados."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Monster Hunt","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In einer längst vergangenen Welt im alten China waren die Reiche der Monster und der Menschen streng voneinander getrennt. Im Reich der Monster herrschen riesige Tyrannen, die jede Rebellion unterdrücken. Alle Hoffnungen liegen auf einer Versöhnung mit den Menschen und einem neuen Königssohn, den die vertriebene Königin bald zur Welt bringen soll. Sie flieht in das Reich der Menschen, um das erwartete Neugeborene zu schützen. Dort gerät sie in die Hände menschlicher Monsterjäger, doch mit einem magischen Trick gibt sie dem ungeborenen Prinzen die Chance, leben zu können, indem sie ihn einem Menschen übergibt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Szörnyvadászat","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A cuki szörnycsemete, Huba egy ember és egy szörny-királynő kapcsolatából született. A kis lény retteg az emberektől, akik üldözik anyja családját, de a hatalmat átvenni készülő, a népük újjászületésében reménykedő szörnyek nézeteivel sem érez rokonszenvet. A barátságos Huba komoly dilemmát él át hovatartozását illetően."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Monster Hunt","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Σε ένα φανταστικό βασίλειο, οι άνθρωποι και τα τέρατα, που κάποτε πολέμησαν μεταξύ τους με τελικούς νικητές τους πρώτους, ζουν τώρα σε σχετική ηρεμία, ξεχωριστά, στους προκαθορισμένους τόπους τους. Η γαλήνη αυτή όμως διαταράσσεται όταν ένα πραξικόπημα στον κόσμο των τεράτων, αναγκάζει την έγκυο βασίλισσα να καταφύγει στον κόσμο των ανθρώπων, μαζί με δύο πιστούς ακόλουθους, τον Ζου Γκάο και την σύζυγό του, Πανγκ Γινγκ...  Η σουρεαλιστική κωμωδία «Monster Hunt» αφηγείται την ιστορία ενός μωρού-τέρατος, του Huba, σε μια φανταστική χώρα που παραπέμπει στην αρχαία κίνα."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Canavar Avı","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bebek canavar Huba, canavar kraliçe ve insan adamdan doğma bir çocuktur. Canavarlar kendilerini sevmeyenler tarafından tehdit unsurudur. Bunu bilen canavarlar, yeni doğanları yakalamayı amaç edinmişlerdir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Лов на чудовища","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"モンスター・ハント","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"妖怪の世界で内戦が勃発し、王族は新たな王から追われる身となってしまう。妊娠していた王妃は人間界へと逃げ出し、小さな村の村長であるテンインに子供を託す。やがてテンインの腹部に子が宿り、それを知った新王の配下と妖怪ハンターの双方に狙われる。妖怪ハンターの女性ショウランに助けてもらいながら、王子のフーバを産んだテンイン。彼とショウランは愛らしいフーバを自分たちの子供のように育てるが、次から次へと追手が襲ってくる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Mi monstruo favorito","runtime":0,"tagline":"Mi monstruo favorito","homepage":"","overview":"El hijo de la realeza del clan de los monstruos es amenazado por los cazadores de criaturas que impiden que se mezclen con los humanos. El hijo de un famoso espadachín, pero poco dotado para el heroísmo, terminará siendo el encargado de proteger al heredero del trono, enfrentándose a monstruos malignos, cazamonstruos y otros enemigos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"捉妖記","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"很久以前，人與萬物共存，當中也包括妖。 但人想獨佔天下，於是人向妖宣戰，把他們趕進了深山大澤，從此人和妖劃界而治。 一天，一對神祕夫婦(曾志偉、吳君如 分飾)與懷有小妖王的妖后逃到永寧村，遇上了善良的天蔭以及降妖少女、二錢天師小嵐，天蔭更陰差陽錯下成為「孕夫」誕下小妖王胡巴。 葛千戶重金懸賞小妖王。 小嵐為了得到賞金，硬拉著天蔭離開永寧村展開了一段奇幻旅程，途中遭遇大押店老闆娘、廚子天師(姚晨 飾)等各路人物。 可愛的小妖王胡巴出生，令天蔭和小嵐關係起了奇妙變化，同時也揭發了一個重大秘密......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"捉妖記","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"很久以前，人與萬物共存，當中也包括妖。\r 但人想獨佔天下，於是人向妖宣戰，把他們趕進了深山大澤，從此人和妖劃界而治。\r 一天，一對神秘夫婦 (曾志偉、吳君如 分飾) 與懷有小妖王的妖後逃到永寧村，遇上了善良的天蔭 (井柏然 飾) 以及降妖少女、二錢天師小嵐 (白百何 飾)，天蔭更陰差陽錯下成為「孕夫」誕下小妖王胡巴。\r 葛千戶 (鍾漢良 飾) 重金懸賞小妖王。\r 小嵐為了得到賞金，硬拉著天蔭離開永寧村展開了一段奇幻旅程，途中遭遇大押店老闆娘 (湯唯 飾)、廚子天師 (姚晨 飾) 等各路人物。\r 可愛的小妖王胡巴出生，令天蔭和小嵐關係起了奇妙變化，同時也揭發了一個重大秘密. ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Caça ao Monstro","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Numa realidade alternativa na qual seres humanos e monstros coexistem, a rainha dos monstros engravida um humano. Da união nasce Huba, um híbrido entre as duas raças que enfrenta hostilidades vinda de ambos os lados."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"צייד המפלצות","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"מפלצת קטנה וצעירה מנסה לעשות שלום בין עולם האנוש לעולם המפלצות"},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Zhuo Yao Ji","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Het verhaal speelt zich af in een wereld waar de mensheid al generaties lang in oorlog is met monsters. Woba is de laatste van de koninklijke bloedlijn van het koninkrijk der monsters. Hij begint aan een missie de twee rassen te verenigen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Polowanie na potwory","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Wuba jest dzieckiem człowieka i królowej potworów. Inne stwory oraz ludzie, widząc w nim zagrożenie, postanawiają go zgładzić."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Truy Lùng Quái Yêu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Truy Lùng Quái Yêu là một bộ phim hành động giả tưởng và vui nhộn về một thế giới khi người và yêu cùng tồn tại. Trong cuộc chiến khốc liệt giữa loài người và yêu quái, mối quan hệ của Thiên Âm và Tiểu Lam cũng dần dần có sự thay đổi. Đồng thời, những bí mật kinh thiên động địa cũng dần sáng tỏ."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Monstrų medžioklė","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Senajame pasaulyje, kai monstrai ir žmonės gyveno atskirose karalystėse, gimė kūdikis, kurio tėvai – monstrų karalienė ir žmogus. Paskutinė karališkosios monstrų šeimos palikuonė, vardu Vuba, tampa tiek monstrų, tiek žmonių taikiniu. Ar mielam kūdikiui pavyks išgyventi ir suvienyti du visiškai skirtingus pasaulius?"},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Lov na príšery","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"شکار هیولا 1","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان درباره یک بچه هیولای بامزه است که پدرش انسان و مادرش یک هیولا است، اما حالا هم از طرف انسان ها و هم هیولاها مورد هجوم قرار گرفته و…"},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Monster Hunt","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"El fill de la reialesa del clan dels monstres és amenaçat pels caçadors de criatures que impedeixen que es barregin amb els humans. El fill d’un famós espadatxí, però poc dotat per a l’heroisme, acabarà sent l’encarregat de protegir l’hereu del tron, enfrontant-se a monstres malignes, caçamostres i altres enemics."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"563a4ef7c3a3681b54023a92","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/563a4ef7c3a3681b54023a92","author":"Reno","content":"$11","created_at":"2015-11-04T18:31:19.185Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:18:27.268Z","author_details":{"name":"Reno","rating":7,"username":"Rangan","avatar_path":"/6ZpVUJzqXMzH35VprEtnX0sNI3.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":497984,"adult":false,"title":"Monster Hunt 2","video":false,"overview":"The sequel to Monster Hunt. Set in a world where monsters and humans co-exist, the franchise tells the story of Wuba, a baby monster born to be king. Wuba becomes the central figure in stopping an all-out monster civil war.","genre_ids":[12,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8865,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/3IxcMNvnDKDKFpLzMH73LwnbXAm.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-16","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/gKDuRB6Uj3gzF8Dd85DOtkxi7KC.jpg","original_title":"捉妖记2","original_language":"zh"},{"id":344938,"adult":false,"title":"The Ark Of Mr. Chow","video":false,"overview":"A group of bright teenagers are recruited for a special college program for young geniuses only to find themselves socially awkward among their more normal peers.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3739,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/e9WJAGboE8RYg5DR6D1EHOxB1NF.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-19","vote_average":4.842,"backdrop_path":"/tb6EjnHwEn1P861MCyqSsnAxRNs.jpg","original_title":"少年班","original_language":"zh"},{"id":174688,"adult":false,"title":"The Trials of Muhammad Ali","video":false,"overview":"Brash boxer Cassius Clay burst into the American consciousness in the early 1960s, just ahead of the Civil Rights movement. His transformation into the spiritually enlightened heavyweight champion Muhammad Ali is legendary, but this religious awakening also led to a bitter legal battle with the U.S. government after he refused to serve in the Vietnam War. This film reveals the perfect storm of race, religion and politics that shaped one of the most recognizable figures in sports history.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.073,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/cTwIWk5RpPgBz35J3sWBxSgo6uP.jpg","release_date":"2013-08-23","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/bN3CezQKJmNBy8Q1PutGHzHDbBi.jpg","original_title":"The Trials of Muhammad Ali","original_language":"en"},{"id":327476,"adult":false,"title":"Reunion","video":false,"overview":"Luokkakokous is a story about three men that travel back to their hometown to attend their high school class reunion.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1236,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/bQ1SKVLmN5HDNPAAlH9o48SYYtz.jpg","release_date":"2015-02-25","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/2HI6PbPaONpSaoif44INBf5jR87.jpg","original_title":"Luokkakokous","original_language":"fi"},{"id":79151,"adult":false,"title":"Love You You","video":false,"overview":"A paralegal is sent on a undercover mission to inspect the young owner of a stunning beach resort for illegal practices. The pair bicker and fight, but the rules of attraction says otherwise...","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3059,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/ofo0yDbZyk4NvndIWbIkKJp7DWF.jpg","release_date":"2011-10-13","vote_average":6.636,"backdrop_path":"/olPW6bbZCXEoXF7QVgjnlzYAJJg.jpg","original_title":"夏日乐悠悠","original_language":"zh"},{"id":93412,"adult":false,"title":"Golden Chicken 2","video":false,"overview":"The year is 2046 and 82 year old Golden Chicken Kum, spots a heartbroken man planning to take memory loss-pills. Claiming that Hong Kong people have a way of forgetting, she begins to recap part of her life story, starting in 2003 during a time where she was desperately looking for a husband and the SARS outbreak happened.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7449,"vote_count":17,"poster_path":"/hgJLMYPpOKiwKQmQzHVuEaS91RW.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-24","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/cJmZYwLw7llzvciEpMYEaNfpoDc.jpg","original_title":"金雞2","original_language":"cn"},{"id":361974,"adult":false,"title":"Kids vs Monsters","video":false,"overview":"The six richest people in the world each have one thing still dragging them down.. their intolerable kids. Luckily, there is a mysterious entity that is happy to help. See, he has some monsters of his own and they are just dying to test out their skills.. One house. Six kids. Seven monsters. Who will be left standing? It's time for a showdown.. it's Kids Vs Monsters!","genre_ids":[14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3166,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/4G6yxAxvZjSk06aDXfDOfnsqlUB.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-29","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Kids vs Monsters","original_language":"en"},{"id":333759,"adult":false,"title":"Let's Get Married","video":false,"overview":"The stories of four couples reflect Chinese views on love and marriage.","genre_ids":[10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4343,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/yRdR6B9ClIT4LSKkpk2hPczff49.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-02","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/8paPjT3vhLgnkOmgfbe08Ogbk8Y.jpg","original_title":"咱们结婚吧","original_language":"zh"},{"id":382063,"adult":false,"title":"Clifford the Big Red Dog: Look Out, Clifford! and Big Fun in the Sun","video":true,"overview":"Clifford the Big Red Dog: Look Out, Clifford!","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0297,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/sKRlLcoL42PFHNHCGnO0gXItsQr.jpg","release_date":"2003-06-23","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Clifford the Big Red Dog: Look Out, Clifford! and Big Fun in the Sun","original_language":"en"},{"id":875279,"adult":false,"title":"One More Shot","video":false,"overview":"After his wife's death professional bodyguard Lung Wei went overseas to find doctors for his daughter, but instead found a new job as a virtual reality tester.","genre_ids":[28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6879,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/NwORQmefgrKPfo5eQ3gp8sVAWD.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-13","vote_average":5.681,"backdrop_path":"/j4ya52FqogRzqNVGDhrp9k0iNNQ.jpg","original_title":"神兵特攻","original_language":"zh"},{"id":251749,"adult":false,"title":"The Four 2","video":false,"overview":"The four constables Emotionless, Iron Hands , Life Snatcher and ColdBlood are specially skilled in their own individual super powers. When the four constables of the Divine Constabulary investigate a murder in the suburbs, they unexpectedly stumble on clues to the murder of Emotionless's family 15 years ago.","genre_ids":[28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4917,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/keINQqFnbovPS5NuYFhgeE1i5Rv.jpg","release_date":"2013-11-21","vote_average":6.831,"backdrop_path":"/gucBjmUkdr5GgRz2ookMLLWQngd.jpg","original_title":"四大名捕2","original_language":"zh"},{"id":412190,"adult":false,"title":"Love O2O","video":false,"overview":"A college stud tries to level up his relationship with a computer science major after becoming attracted to her skills in an online role-playing game.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5157,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/5CLPSenC8TY9slwaSCXQGJ5UclO.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-12","vote_average":6.669,"backdrop_path":"/cfAsueSHK0hbSQe8jAnUgF8eOtj.jpg","original_title":"微微一笑很傾城","original_language":"zh"},{"id":345235,"adult":false,"title":"Monk Comes Down the Mountain","video":false,"overview":"A monk leaves his monastery and ventures out into the real world for the first time in his life, and ends up in an adventure with a kung-fu master who is guarding a special artifact.","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1927,"vote_count":108,"poster_path":"/eS2wMBnOCBUB3g58andUYIVkICF.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-03","vote_average":5.111,"backdrop_path":"/rHjNt4SbHYg0Mhs6LTyGWaH7wgA.jpg","original_title":"道士下山","original_language":"zh"},{"id":191421,"adult":false,"title":"So Young","video":false,"overview":"Although new friendships and new love await her, a college freshman discovers that university life is not as simple as she had hoped.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6315,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/6o4AfophJBHV9mC7w7eYXyMMnh1.jpg","release_date":"2013-04-26","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/xUsXFOKjlE66OupngZcJE2WaKV0.jpg","original_title":"致我们终将逝去的青春","original_language":"zh"},{"id":351694,"adult":false,"title":"Monkey King: Hero Is Back","video":false,"overview":"The all-powerful Monkey King once roamed freely between Heaven and Earth, but after angering the Gods, he was imprisoned within an ice cage deep within the mountains. 500 years later, monsters attack a small village and a child flees to the mountains. Unknowingly, the child releases the Monkey King from his curse. With the help and encouragement from this special child, Monkey King saves the village from the evil monsters.","genre_ids":[14,16,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7189,"vote_count":286,"poster_path":"/xHme10Y5jVdH8KeSGgStndjatF5.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-10","vote_average":6.925,"backdrop_path":"/xESy6kg2k4JsGzHU0ILkOL9qYec.jpg","original_title":"西游记之大圣归来","original_language":"zh"},{"id":384112,"adult":false,"title":"Dad in Training","video":false,"overview":"Following the breakdown of his marriage, a self-involved man begins to embrace fatherhood.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2777,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/jbYyGrDIssr5Y5D8yVvOiBq0tmf.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-06","vote_average":6.115,"backdrop_path":"/rpzcT8PfP44AbRkuWwMhxyk0g5i.jpg","original_title":"Tout pour être heureux","original_language":"fr"},{"id":117352,"adult":false,"title":"Crayon Shin-chan: Super-Dimension! The Storm Called My Bride","video":false,"overview":"Shin-chan is approached by his time-traveling future bride-to-be Tamiko, who asks him to help save his adult self from the ruler of Neo Tokio.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4637,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/zUoLr4wvk45t19HdrNWFGp0RtbG.jpg","release_date":"2010-04-17","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/snDGwQ3fbfNiGwUfT7dVPQ4MTSV.jpg","original_title":"クレヨンしんちゃん 超時空！嵐を呼ぶオラの花嫁","original_language":"ja"},{"id":865140,"adult":false,"title":"Chilangolandia","video":false,"overview":"Mexico City, or \"Chilangolandia,\" is a chaotic metropolis where millions of stories take place every day. Some of them are part of this fun comedy full of familiar characters and others that defy stereotypes. Ramiro is a taxi driver who hopes his problems will end when his nephew \"El Chulo\" becomes a national soccer star. On the other hand, Carmen and Miguel are couple who unexpectedly receive a suitcase with a large sum of money, just what they need to get out of their financial situation. But when the true owners of the cash realize that it fell into the wrong hands, endless adventures and misunderstandings break out within this complex city.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3562,"vote_count":109,"poster_path":"/gNObb3Q1P2yO2Z14bs6AXx0cWVy.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-16","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7FPgSnAeAhVPlg38Y0XJs6EopcL.jpg","original_title":"Chilangolandia","original_language":"es"},{"id":424632,"adult":false,"title":"Until Forever","video":false,"overview":"Until Forever: The Michael Boyum Story is a powerful, true account of one young man's courageous battle with leukemia and his journey of faith.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4171,"vote_count":117,"poster_path":"/643I1ehH8ldJ7QtWiY6qtegQ1o5.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-20","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/tgqyVeDfnqLt17v7Y8vagr5M4cS.jpg","original_title":"Until Forever","original_language":"en"},{"id":282070,"adult":false,"title":"Parasyte: Part 2","video":false,"overview":"Humanity is under attack by human-mimicking flesh-eating alien parasites. One parasite bonds with his young high school student host, and he convinces the parasite to help him stop the others.","genre_ids":[878,27,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7333,"vote_count":205,"poster_path":"/qO8zQ9dSADWiwRnR7oCOsPDuOom.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-25","vote_average":7.054,"backdrop_path":"/vT4bg2mKaJ3cPLxlwotuewC0LZk.jpg","original_title":"寄生獣 完結編","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":58,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","video":false,"overview":"Jack's got a blood debt to pay: he owes his soul to the legendary Davy Jones, ghastly Ruler of the Ocean Depths.  But ever-crafty Jack isn't about to go down without a fight.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":13.4319,"vote_count":16905,"poster_path":"/uXEqmloGyP7UXAiphJUu2v2pcuE.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-06","vote_average":7.374,"backdrop_path":"/vr6n6ZFUZvedvIlhfYcbCWcaKyW.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","original_language":"en"},{"id":271075,"adult":false,"title":"Attack of the Brainsucker","video":false,"overview":"Samantha, a little girl growing up in the sixties, loves classic b-movies and monsters - That is, until they start to invade her bedroom and her obssession compels her parents to seek help from the latest scientific breakthrough","genre_ids":[14,27,878],"popularity":0.1983,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/5ufqdk3zErIhIhDCGsWSWnU6E8M.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-28","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/jogZjxsXBEdjZJ6z3GksooOmIwB.jpg","original_title":"Attack of the Brainsucker","original_language":"en"},{"id":3126,"adult":false,"title":"Alvin and the Chipmunks Meet Frankenstein","video":false,"overview":"The Chipmunks work in an amusement park attraction. After Alvin drives a crazy tour group, they miss their next performance and are locked in the park after closing time. Little do they know that the real Dr. Frankenstein has been hired in a new attraction called, \"Frankenstein's Castle\"; figuring that the castle isn't scary enough, the mad scientist recreates the real Monster.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"popularity":0.8982,"vote_count":153,"poster_path":"/hiXOFmWtxQ3LdrGgP2uOuR1DHBp.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-04","vote_average":6.739,"backdrop_path":"/vsLwmFVWKg1qydVJDX5sA5psiCa.jpg","original_title":"Alvin and the Chipmunks Meet Frankenstein","original_language":"en"},{"id":3034,"adult":false,"title":"Young Frankenstein","video":false,"overview":"A young neurosurgeon inherits the castle of his grandfather, the famous Dr. Victor von Frankenstein. In the castle he finds a funny hunchback, a pretty lab assistant and the elderly housekeeper. Young Frankenstein believes that the work of his grandfather was delusional, but when he discovers the book where the mad doctor described his reanimation experiment, he suddenly changes his mind.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":4.3245,"vote_count":3348,"poster_path":"/3BvvVKPg9yucChlSvQtJxAbLmj9.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-15","vote_average":7.855,"backdrop_path":"/wKSJLUgJtCMSZOIU1By8g5FSaHk.jpg","original_title":"Young Frankenstein","original_language":"en"},{"id":6974,"adult":false,"title":"The Angry Red Planet","video":false,"overview":"The first manned flight to Mars returns after having been out of communications since it had arrived on Mars. What would it reveal?","genre_ids":[12,878,27],"popularity":0.4792,"vote_count":79,"poster_path":"/jtY9aJjUdbw6CaQ3rHQW6WJKB6g.jpg","release_date":"1959-11-23","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/tL96NSWrcmkcBEH7JVt7x5Jhnwh.jpg","original_title":"The Angry Red Planet","original_language":"en"},{"id":1258450,"adult":false,"title":"Camping Idéal","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[14],"popularity":1.023,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/sb9ykEYAKmFAjzWyhrJXzrFhw0C.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-07","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Camping Idéal","original_language":"fr"},{"id":585,"adult":false,"title":"Monsters, Inc.","video":false,"overview":"Lovable Sulley and his wisecracking sidekick Mike Wazowski are the top scare team at Monsters, Inc., the scream-processing factory in Monstropolis. When a little girl named Boo wanders into their world, it's the monsters who are scared silly, and it's up to Sulley and Mike to keep her out of sight and get her back home.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"popularity":15.8487,"vote_count":19500,"poster_path":"/wFSpyMsp7H0ttERbxY7Trlv8xry.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-01","vote_average":7.846,"backdrop_path":"/sDTnMOJ3H5wI38OxObmCtK7wfd5.jpg","original_title":"Monsters, Inc.","original_language":"en"},{"id":1063707,"adult":false,"title":"The Demojordan","video":false,"overview":"A frightening creature from unknown depths rises to attack a lone teenager.","genre_ids":[27,28,35],"popularity":0.1699,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/bINsCMadLeI3v8aq2vLcuJKodbK.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-04","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/bBQhH58IujVMhDp1uT9ABs0ILxl.jpg","original_title":"The Demojordan","original_language":"en"},{"id":4407,"adult":false,"title":"The Three Investigators in The Secret of Skeleton Island","video":false,"overview":"The hobby detectives “The Three Investigators” want to take a little break. So they take advantage of an offer from Peter's father, who has accepted a job in South Africa and wants to take the detectives there. But Jupiter, Peter and Bob wouldn't be the three investigators marks feared by the criminal world if they just lounged around in the sun on their vacation. So it's no wonder that the clever boys soon have their next case to solve...","genre_ids":[9648,12,10751],"popularity":0.6828,"vote_count":67,"poster_path":"/6fSy3VGyC0JHlUC2cG1vl36QiqI.jpg","release_date":"2007-11-07","vote_average":6.119,"backdrop_path":"/s0gmpE2gWOiN0yZvHRYJ6YTdpsW.jpg","original_title":"Die drei ??? – Das Geheimnis der Geisterinsel","original_language":"de"},{"id":4365,"adult":false,"title":"Munchies","video":false,"overview":"Simon Watterman, a space archaeologist, discovers the \"Munchies\" in a cave in Peru. Cecil Watterman, Simon's evil twin brother and snack food entrepreneur, kidnaps the creature. What Cecil does not know is that the creature, when chopped up, regenerates into many new creatures and are they mean!","genre_ids":[35,27,878],"popularity":3.4931,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/51eGxEkyGMcHSGDLRjnf1oOKx2W.jpg","release_date":"1987-03-01","vote_average":4.764,"backdrop_path":"/iGaaukuyOnRgGpvGYxJQ4KGsihL.jpg","original_title":"Munchies","original_language":"en"},{"id":4398,"adult":false,"title":"Lissi and the Wild Emperor","video":false,"overview":"The plot concerns a yeti who makes a pact with the devil to kidnap the most beautiful girl in the world. This turns out to be the Princess Lissi, who is clearly the Austrian Princess and later Empress Elisabeth of Bavaria, and much of the film is taken up with subplots related to the court and to the romantic relationship between Elisabeth and her husband. The film is thus a comic parody of the Sissi films.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.3269,"vote_count":194,"poster_path":"/eRqDnWHKPgbJ0yMaGd89sdrA3oU.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-24","vote_average":5.861,"backdrop_path":"/3BRjyNkBwDKNi4h2AghKTgYywHp.jpg","original_title":"Lissi und der wilde Kaiser","original_language":"de"},{"id":9626,"adult":false,"title":"Red Sonja","video":false,"overview":"The tyrant Gedren seeks the total power in a world of barbarism. She raids the city Hablac and kills the keeper of a talisman that gives her great power. Red Sonja, sister of the keeper, sets out with her magic sword to overthrow Gedren.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":2.6604,"vote_count":918,"poster_path":"/83v0W5cCSFsWpI0cAj8DRlihySN.jpg","release_date":"1985-04-09","vote_average":5.371,"backdrop_path":"/iWFnany1vDQ4EoBgvm7E3Pb0RyS.jpg","original_title":"Red Sonja","original_language":"en"},{"id":464768,"adult":false,"title":"Junk Head","video":false,"overview":"Mankind can no longer reproduce because of gene manipulation aimed at making life longer. The clones ruling the bottomless underworld may have become fertile. Parton is selected to go on a mission through a subterranean labyrinth crawling with monsters to secure humanity's future.","genre_ids":[16,878,28,12],"popularity":1.2619,"vote_count":57,"poster_path":"/t1pHIeZZGmr8TWMyn7r1TGoMnMo.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-18","vote_average":6.57,"backdrop_path":"/aAdTgf8fAc8P0o6wLD51o2oYoRP.jpg","original_title":"JUNK HEAD","original_language":"ja"},{"id":856289,"adult":false,"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","video":false,"overview":"Based on the most well-known classical fantasy novel of China, Fengshenyanyi, the trilogy is a magnificent eastern high fantasy epic that recreates the prolonged mythical wars between humans, immortals and monsters, which happened more than three thousand years ago.","genre_ids":[28,14,10752],"popularity":6.5727,"vote_count":467,"poster_path":"/6VOV2wU3WEyN0H1QtrbAS6whXPc.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-15","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/ef9dYKxDe2isgNhoJsGrt9yjXPz.jpg","original_title":"封神第一部：朝歌风云","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1693,"adult":false,"title":"Monster Man","video":false,"overview":"Two guys and a female hitchhiker are terrorized by a monstrous looking man driving a giant monster truck.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":0.474,"vote_count":126,"poster_path":"/iFCta7mFC7aVTPMA3opH8Vq62Pn.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-30","vote_average":5.976,"backdrop_path":"/s5PmaZuvj7vajfavnNhQazHnovc.jpg","original_title":"Monster Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":1884,"adult":false,"title":"The Ewok Adventure","video":false,"overview":"Wicket the Ewok and his friends agree to help two shipwrecked human children, Mace and Cindel, on a quest to find their parents.","genre_ids":[12,10751,14,878,10770],"popularity":1.6742,"vote_count":408,"poster_path":"/4GrECLKaJhYA6ooSTOG0XEuPnSl.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-21","vote_average":5.868,"backdrop_path":"/waWPYcXrbENXEoJkrQt7zFUdq14.jpg","original_title":"The Ewok Adventure","original_language":"en"},{"id":466942,"adult":false,"title":"Basilisk","video":false,"overview":"A lizard man tries to get to a treasure island while chased by a sea monster.","genre_ids":[12,16],"popularity":0.1664,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/iJgvpA03RuBIUgcDzTj4cFRukVb.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-06","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Basilisk","original_language":"en"},{"id":2929,"adult":false,"title":"Frankenstein","video":false,"overview":"Frankenstein, a young medical student, trying to create the perfect human being, instead creates a misshapen monster. Made ill by what he has done, Frankenstein is comforted by his fiancée; but on his wedding night he is visited by the monster.","genre_ids":[27,878,14],"popularity":1.4474,"vote_count":224,"poster_path":"/xPzF7qW6FFZEzfsnsKqNOncxJNU.jpg","release_date":"1910-03-18","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/vqZEHv2KxjyVXjbtMhIDIZ6xoLf.jpg","original_title":"Frankenstein","original_language":"en"},{"id":2969,"adult":false,"title":"A Daughter Of Destiny","video":false,"overview":"Hanns Heinz Ewers' grim science-fiction novel Alraune has already been filmed twice when this version was assembled in 1928. In another of his \"mad doctor\" roles, Paul Wegener plays Professor Brinken, sociopathic scientist who combines the genes of an executed murderer with those of a prostitute. The result is a beautiful young woman named Alraune (Brigitte Helm), who is incapable of feeling any real emotions -- least of all guilt or regret. Upon attaining adulthood, Alraune sets about to seduce and destroy every male who crosses her path. Ultimately, Professor Brinken is hoist on his own petard when he falls hopelessly in love with Alraune himself. Alraune was remade in 1930, with Brigitte Helm repeating her role, and again in 1951, with Hildegarde Knef as the \"heroine\" and Erich von Stroheim as her misguided mentor.","genre_ids":[18,14,878,27],"popularity":0.2822,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/iiyGr1iO8DEDEOlFKCImUSnqYR6.jpg","release_date":"1928-01-25","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/rKdOol4W1AzkGPZXLsMNcPWrVSK.jpg","original_title":"Alraune","original_language":"de"},{"id":1062722,"adult":false,"title":"Frankenstein","video":false,"ov